{{Main article|1924年古巴飓风}}
10月13日晚至次日清晨，北洪都拉斯东北偏东方向的西加勒比海形成热带气旋，强度达到热带风暴下限<ref name="HURDAT" />。气旋缓慢向西北偏西移动，于10月15日逐渐转向北上。风暴当天稳步增强，于10月17日达到飓风标准，10月19日又强化成[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]，接下来以持续风速每小时195公里强度吹袭古巴[[比那尔德里奥省|比那尔德里奥省]]。10月20日，飓风因[[高压脊|高压脊]]南下而转向东北偏东。<ref name="MWR" />气旋急剧减弱，以一级飓风强度从佛罗里达州西南部的[[那不勒斯_(佛罗里达州)|那不勒斯]]附近登陆<ref name="NOAA1">{{cite report | author1 = Eric S. Blake | author2 = Edward N. Rappaport | author3 = Christopher W. Landsea | year = 2006 | title = The Deadliest, Costliest, and Most Intense United States Tropical Cyclones (1851 to 2006) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2017-01-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/NWS-TPC-5.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221141759/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/NWS-TPC-5.pdf | archivedate = 2016-12-21 | deadurl = no | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref>，接下来又以风力时速110公里强度从[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]北部进入大西洋。风暴在穿越西大西洋期间稳步减弱，最终于10月23日在百慕大西南偏西方向逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />经过2009年3月的重新分析，气象学界认定风暴属[[五级大西洋飓风列表|五级大西洋飓风]]，最大持续风速高达每小时270公里，最低气压910毫巴（百帕，27英寸汞柱）<ref>{{cite report | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2009-03 | accessdate = 2017-01-02 | archivedate = 2016-12-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161224102747/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/data_sub/re_anal.html | title = Re-Analysis Project; March 2009 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/data_sub/re_anal.html }}</ref>。

古巴至少有90人遇难<ref name="Cuba">{{cite web | url = http://www.cubahurricanes.org/history-hurricanes-chronicles.php | title = Cuba Hurricanes Historic Threats | publisher = CubaHurricanes.org | accessdate = 2017-01-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161023015936/http://cubahurricanes.org/history-hurricanes-chronicles.php | archivedate = 2016-10-23 }}</ref>，该国西部各地的庄稼和建筑受到重创，[[曼图阿_(古巴)|曼图阿]]有50至100人受伤<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="OaklandTribune">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | year = 1924 | title = 12 Killed, 100 Hurt in Hurricane in Florida | newspaper = Oakland Tribune}}</ref>。面对风暴威胁，佛罗里达州的部分船只提前固定，树木及时修剪<ref name="Barnes" />。基韦斯特的阵风时速最高，有105公里，但植被受到的破坏程度很轻<ref name="MWR" />。气旋令佛罗里达州南部普降暴雨，其中[[马可岛|马可岛]]降雨量最高，达590毫米<ref name="Barnes">{{cite book | last = Barnes | first = Jay | year = 1998 | title = Florida's Hurricane History | url = https://archive.org/details/floridashurrican0000barn_g4v2 | page = [https://archive.org/details/floridashurrican0000barn_g4v2/page/108 108]}}</ref>。降水令[[棕榈滩县|棕榈滩县]]爆发洪灾，公路和铁路运输受到影响。该县测得112毫米雨量，创下15年来新高。佛罗里达州南部本土的最强阵风时速为110公里，部分从该州东南部出发的海上旅游行程取消。[[麦尔兹堡|麦尔兹堡]]和[[蓬塔戈尔达_(佛罗里达州)|蓬塔戈尔达]]的电报线路中断，不过整体破坏程度很轻。<ref name="SanAntonio">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | year = 1924 | title = Gulf Tornado Takes 13 Lives-50 are Injured | newspaper = The San Antonio Express}}</ref>
